"author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "liquidity_hunter_app_dashboard_data__reanchor_bos_close_break", "label": "_reanchor_bos_close_break", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Composition-level conservative close-break confirmation: re-times each BOS to the first candle that closes beyond the formed level it broke and drops wick-only breaks, matching the macro SMC cycle; long event-free stretches are intended."}, {"id": "liquidity_hunter_app_dashboard_data__drop_pre_break_reference_bos", "label": "_drop_pre_break_reference_bos", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "A wick that pokes beyond a still-unbroken prior BOS level ratchets the staircase extreme, so the next continuation BOS would reference a pre-break wick attempt; a reference may only come from price action after the prior break confirms."}, {"id": "liquidity_hunter_app_narrative_narrativeengine", "label": "NarrativeEngine", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Lives in app/ (not psychology/) because it depends on outputs from every layer; runs last via dataclasses.replace since it needs the fully assembled DashboardData."}, {"id": "liquidity_hunter_api_routes_dashboard_dashboard", "label": "GET /api/dashboard route", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "liquidity_hunter_api_cache_ttlcache", "label": "TTLCache", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "CLAUDE.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "liquidity_hunter_api_schema